        <abstract> 
<p>Has given CD’s queries about expression to W. H. Stirling. Thomas Bridges, the catechist, had previously answered some questions incompletely [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">2643</hi>]; BJS forwards them [see <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>].</p> 
            <p>BJS answers CD’s query about when some calves show their adult colour.</p>
